<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 jiǔ shí jiǔ zhǐ xiǎo yáng yǐ zài ān quán de de fāng, hái yǒu yī zhǐ xiǎo yáng bù zhī liú luò zài hé fāng.
 mù rén de xīn zhōng jí qí yōu shāng, tā zài dào chù xún zhǎo nà zhǐ yáng.
 nǐ shì fǒu jiù shì nà zhǐ mí shī de yáng, nǐ shì fǒu jiù shì nà zhǐ mí shī de yáng?
 zhǔ zài fān shān yuè lǐng xún zhǎo hū huàn nǐ, kuài kuài huí dào zhǔ de shēn páng.</lyrics>
<title>nǐ shì fǒu jiù shì nà zhǐ mí shī de yáng 迦南1204</title>
</song>